=== Raspberry Pi: Manual Setup Required ===

The following tools are not available via apt and need manual installation.
Check each project's install page for the recommended method:

  fish       https://fishshell.com
  mise       https://mise.jdx.dev
  starship   https://starship.rs
  atuin      https://atuin.sh
  uv         https://docs.astral.sh/uv
  neovim     https://github.com/neovim/neovim/releases (apt version is usually outdated)
  fzf        https://github.com/junegunn/fzf
  ffmpeg     apt install ffmpeg

Update run_once_after_raspberry-setup-note.sh.tmpl once you've settled on install methods.

===========================================

EOF
